00:00:09.460 --> 00:00:11.460
- [Narrator] We are the paradoxical ape.

00:00:12.360 --> 00:00:14.910
Bipedal, naked.

00:00:14.910 --> 00:00:15.770
Large-brained.

00:00:17.550 --> 00:00:20.570
Long the master of fire,
tools and language.

00:00:21.650 --> 00:00:23.790
But still trying to understand ourselves.

00:00:25.910 --> 00:00:27.720
Aware that death is inevitable,

00:00:29.230 --> 00:00:30.690
yet filled with optimism.

00:00:32.530 --> 00:00:33.550
We grow up slowly.

00:00:34.890 --> 00:00:36.040
We hand down knowledge.

00:00:37.480 --> 00:00:39.110
We empathize and deceive.

00:00:40.950 --> 00:00:42.380
We shape the future from our

00:00:42.380 --> 00:00:44.540
shared understanding of the past.

00:00:46.380 --> 00:00:50.180
CARTA brings together experts
from diverse disciplines

00:00:50.180 --> 00:00:54.530
to exchange insights on who
we are, and how we got here.

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:57.980
An exploration made possible

00:00:57.980 --> 00:01:00.520
by the generosity of humans like you.

